# Trinity Initialization & Mistral Trigger Plan

This plan outlines the steps to initialize the Trinity workspace and execute the Mistral trigger workflow.

## Proposed Changes

No code changes are proposed. This is an execution-only task.

### Workspace Initialization [trinity_start]
- Run `make info` to verify workspace status.
- Check the current operating phase from [manifest.json](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/manifest.json).
- Run `make seed_wisdom` to populate the knowledge base.

### Mistral Trigger [mistral_trigger]
- Run `python3 scripts/mistral_guardian.py "Initialize workspace and trigger guardian"` (using a default query as none was provided).
- Read [GUARD_ALERT.json](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/GUARD_ALERT.json).
- Apply the verdict according to the workflow rules.

## Verification Plan

